l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而怒人時期佢啲riff solo度得幾正<br />\n<br />\nbtw結他唔可以無意色樓浩南掛<br />\n玩live結他加octave入bass amp呢下真係好iconic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b801c1d76f6de55a38a96aedffa71db168819d0c","tid":2078084,"uid":106745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"Eugene Pao係咪太舊已經無咩人聽過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1c8c814e2c5c513b05a3947ce6c849beb78482","tid":2078084,"uid":371,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"Alan Cheung"},{"pid":"f0ae9fa6b53dcc661ceb1de3ac0063f5607061b4","tid":2078084,"uid":248925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"820bd1ddd0e57e72fcfd7d1fa8f6c208f6b09b8d","tid":2078084,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a9249cf964bc15e07f02fda3ff28ddaba2e7f2f","tid":2078084,"uid":68860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"Mike Orange 編曲一流"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"如果數編曲我會排：<br />\nMike Orange<br />\nSoni@雞翼蒸肉餅<br />\nPer se"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"其實chochukmo lester都勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見啲credit成日去曬mike度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf42a5e40a9fdf71a25df65198f4b342c9277495","tid":2078084,"uid":68860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5bd007b996fc712c7260c202da64e26fd1a1dc0","tid":2078084,"uid":217016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"Jason kui第一？唔係話佢唔勁但唔係名氣大就係最勁架，講真喺香港地好過佢嘅真係唔小"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"Jason Kui 張album 好show off <br />\n好多演嘢嘅成份<br />\n但真係showcase 咗佢嘅唔同skills<br />\n<br />\n<br />